---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Karen Arze | Home">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px;">
    <div style="width: 150px; height: 150px; background: #e1f0ff; border: 5px solid white; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #0056b3;">
      <span>Photo</span>
    </div>
    <h1 style="color: #003366; font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 0;">Karen Arze</h1>
    <p style="color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 10px;">Independent Woman • Optometrist • Mother</p>
  </div>

  <section style="line-height: 1.8; color: #333; margin-bottom: 40px;">
    <p>Quick to adapt and eager to learn, I am reliable enough to take on leadership roles and always strive for work that can model what I would like to see in others. I'm always enthusiastic to apply my experiences into an environment that appreciates organization and efficiency!</p>
  </section>

  <div style="background: #f8fbff; border-radius: 15px; padding: 25px; border-left: 5px solid #a2c2e1; margin-bottom: 40px;">
    <h3 style="color: #003366; margin-top: 0;">Personal Contact</h3>
    <p>📍 <strong>State:</strong> Virginia</p>
    <p>📞 <strong>Phone:</strong> 757-515-****</p>
    <p>✉️ <strong>Email:</strong> karen**********@yahoo.com</p>
  </div>

  <h2 style="color: #003366; text-align: center;">My Interests</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;">
    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #eef2f7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);">
      <h4 style="color: #0056b3; margin-top: 0;">🌊 Beach Walks</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Even if it's a bit of a drive, it's always worth being able to see the beautiful sunrise!</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #eef2f7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px;">
      <h4 style="color: #0056b3; margin-top: 0;">💃 Dancing</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">I know bachata and Meringue; currently practicing Jazz and Salsa. This is when I feel the most like myself!</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #eef2f7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px;">
      <h4 style="color: #0056b3; margin-top: 0;">🍳 Cooking</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">I love being experimental! I challenge myself with what ingredients I have to make something my family will enjoy.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #eef2f7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center;">
      <h4 style="color: #003366; margin-top: 0;">❤️ My Children</h4>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">My Son and Daughter are my pride and joy! They will always be my babies at heart.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
